{"tid":1182353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中學生被問中國需不需要民主,有學生驚被斬","createTime":"2019-06-02T06:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T06:27:13.000Z","uid":96512,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9df6b103db6d8b5ba94bdb5ba39d241801c880","tid":1182353,"uid":96512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"本地生誤當六四是列強侵華<br />\n對中共屠城認知較國際校學生少<br />\n當問及中國是否需要有民主，有25位同學表示需要，並能簡單解釋何謂民主；但仍有多名受訪同學聽到這問題時顯得猶豫，或不想回答。有上水學生的回應是：「我會唔會俾人斬頭㗎？需要嘅，度度都需要㗎嘛。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1kTQVnVABpoeisvfWB/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1kTQVnVABpoeisvfWB%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0b1dba5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190602/20693590?fbclid=IwAR1qLS741gY0nMRhfiolMmKbSoTpa9ZKhmD4OT-vTKUS955aQ2kxFZu21uM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693590%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qLS741gY0nMRhfiolMmKbSoTpa9ZKhmD4OT-vTKUS955aQ2kxFZu21uM&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=dc994f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693590%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qLS741gY0nMRhfiolMmKbSoTpa9ZKhmD4OT-vTKUS955aQ2kxFZu21uM&h=7e74ccb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190602/20693590?fbclid=IwAR1qLS741gY0nMRhfiolMmKbSoTpa9ZKhmD4OT-vTKUS955aQ2kxFZu21uM</a>"},{"pid":"45c0f5ec4b8cf32f90e9c5dd4e13331aeb59df04","tid":1182353,"uid":244543,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"羅同學好大波"},{"pid":"dfbef30d675a62bc561c069afad47611c82e5f96","tid":1182353,"uid":2394